{"tid":2013713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中央電視台算唔算承認左 有武漢P4實驗室科學家 著草去美國？","createTime":"2020-05-12T12:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T13:58:28.000Z","uid":179729,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"acf49a04ad0df292bc71b157274f84b48cb729b3","tid":2013713,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sendvid.com/azc5cd98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fazc5cd98&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=fe1b4f46\" target=\"_blank\">https://sendvid.com/azc5cd98</a><br />\n<br />\n花生會唔會愈黎愈貴？"},{"pid":"d9c0d1161ccacb9487bc70eb6c46f045e140e77b","tid":2013713,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96ccf802437b22cabe140773fa95884867eb462","tid":2013713,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1260176039898161152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1260176039898161152&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=06142a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1260176039898161152&h=ba049cd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1260176039898161152</a><br />\n好多毛毛蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec6e5587207155c5b1d1cc200f8e78412abfe0","tid":2013713,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96ccf802437b22cabe140773fa95884867eb462","tid":2013713,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1260176039898161152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1260176039898161152&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=06142a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1260176039898161152&h=ba049cd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1260176039898161152</a><br />\n好多毛毛蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"好多大陸人反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5673af603baba2926c92d85b21c41bd4e835aa6f","tid":2013713,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"咁都走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2834a75c9077fd68f8073fed347235d254446932","tid":2013713,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tg35Yq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTg35Yq8.png&h=ab7f1530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國賓夕法尼亞州匹茲堡大學（University of Pittsburgh）37歲醫學院助理教授劉彬（Bing Liu，譯音）上周六（5月2日）在家中遭槍殺，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">院方發文悼念指劉彬生前致力研究新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）且「即將有重大發現」</span></strong>；警方周三（6日）進一步透露案情，行兇後懷疑<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">吞槍自盡的是46歲華裔男子顧浩</span></strong>（Hao Gu，音譯），曾因一名親密伴侶與劉彬發生感情糾紛，當局相信這亦是其犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n劉彬是中國籍人士，已婚但沒有子女，父母均住在中國，案發時其妻子不在家，也沒有財物損失。 據英國廣播公司（BBC）中文網報道，疑犯<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>顧浩生前在一間美國上市的跨國能源管理公司工作逾16年，於賓夕法尼亞州分部擔任軟件部門高層。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，當日顧浩去到劉彬在羅斯鎮（Ross Township）的寓所，從一道沒有上鎖的門進內施襲，劉彬頭、頸及身體中槍死亡；其後在距離案發單位約90米，顧浩被發現伏屍在車上，相信他是在犯案後返回座駕吞槍自殺。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，經調查發現顧浩與劉彬相識，且二人曾因一名親密伴侶陷入長期糾紛，故推斷此為顧浩的犯案動機，同時強調「暫時未掌握到線索，顯示此案與劉彬的工作或研究有關」。由於二人均非美國公民，案件現已被轉介有關聯邦部門處理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>曾發表超過30篇研究論文</strong><br />\n案發後，匹茲堡大學醫學院網站曾發表悼文稱，劉彬在研究新型冠狀病毒的感染機制及併發症方面「即將有非常重大的發現，我們將努力完成他的研究，以向其傑出的科學成就致敬，全體科學界都將為他的離世而哀悼。」<br />\n<br />\n匹茲堡大學醫學院計算機與系統生物系（Computational &amp; Systems Biology）負責人巴哈爾（Ivet Bahar）形容劉彬非常有天賦，對於幾個科學項目都甚有貢獻，並在知名期刊上發表過文章，最近則進行新型冠狀病毒的研究，剛開始看到「有趣的成果」；巴哈爾說：「我們非常喜歡他，當聽到他遇害，我們都很震驚。」<br />\n<br />\n大學網站資料顯示，劉彬早年於新加坡國立大學取得電腦科學學士及博士學位，後來於卡內基美隆大學（Carnegie Mellon University）進行博士後研究，生前為匹茲堡大學醫學院計算與系統生物學系的研究助理教授，曾發表超過30篇研究論文。"},{"pid":"11819ef3011aef58618b2e2027390b4d2e66d65e","tid":2013713,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"聽唔明 講咩？"},{"pid":"c98ed66aa28286dc14c87ff36da83fc77029e512","tid":2013713,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"開槍手法好專業"},{"pid":"4cf60bc91fb57fefc72471c206f3a0061913b49d","tid":2013713,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tg35Yq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTg35Yq8.png&h=ab7f1530&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係依條友？\b"},{"pid":"7615dc71bba37f952b56018b4e9c170d1b2e7697","tid":2013713,"uid":179729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11819ef3011aef58618b2e2027390b4d2e66d65e","tid":2013713,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"聽唔明 講咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"美國資助的反華分子被包裝成科學家，偽造證據屈中國<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁"},{"pid":"69d8545401b05ef7e1a7832d7eecf7492f94b019","tid":2013713,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"等details<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af75144f94be6185b5b9913cb8b3b4e93d981fa7","tid":2013713,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}